56:45.852 --> 56:48.120
A beautiful song, indeed!


56:48.120 --> 56:50.190
We would like to conclude 


56:50.190 --> 56:52.192
this program 
by sharing these greetings 


56:52.192 --> 56:55.060
from our brothers and sisters in Mali. 


56:55.060 --> 56:57.963
Mali is located in western Africa, 


56:57.963 --> 57:00.133
reaching well into the Sahara Desert. 


57:00.133 --> 57:03.903
The northern part of the country 
is hot and covered with sand, 


57:03.903 --> 57:07.340
but the southern region, 
which is watered by the Niger River, 


57:07.340 --> 57:11.510
is green with forests and vegetation.


57:11.510 --> 57:15.215
The Witnesses in the country 
have a huge task, 


57:15.215 --> 57:18.417
as the ratio 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses to population 


57:18.417 --> 57:23.155
is about one publisher 
to 59,000 residents. 


57:23.155 --> 57:26.358
Also, the distances are tremendous. 


57:26.358 --> 57:28.995
The approximately 300 publishers 


57:28.995 --> 57:30.997
cover an area more than twice 


57:30.997 --> 57:33.734
the size of the country of France.


57:33.733 --> 57:37.270
Mali is one of the hottest countries 
in the world, 


57:37.270 --> 57:39.438
so some groups and congregations 


57:39.438 --> 57:41.440
hold their meetings outdoors 


57:41.440 --> 57:43.610
under the cool shade of a tree.


57:43.610 --> 57:47.313
Although the official language 
of the country is French, 


57:47.313 --> 57:49.681
most people better understand 


57:49.682 --> 57:52.052
the local language Bambara. 


57:52.052 --> 57:56.622
Thus, most meetings are either 
held or interpreted in Bambara. 


57:56.622 --> 58:00.394
Recently, language classes 
were held in Bomu, 


58:00.393 --> 58:03.730
which is another local language.


58:03.730 --> 58:06.498
Also, the seven publishers 
of the American Sign Language group 


58:06.498 --> 58:08.501
have been assigned to witness 


58:08.502 --> 58:12.505
to the more than 
350,000 people in Mali 


58:12.505 --> 58:14.873
who have 
a hearing impairment.


58:14.873 --> 58:17.910
Last year, the total attendance 
for the Memorial 


58:17.910 --> 58:21.113
was over 1,100 people. 


58:21.113 --> 58:23.348
One man who received an invitation 


58:23.348 --> 58:25.685
walked three kilometers, 


58:25.685 --> 58:28.120
or almost two miles, 
to attend the Memorial 


58:28.120 --> 58:31.723
despite having 
a physical challenge with his foot. 


58:31.723 --> 58:34.126
He is now regular at the meetings 


58:34.127 --> 58:36.829
and is making good progress.


58:36.828 --> 58:40.633
Recently, a new Kingdom Hall 
was built in the capital city. 


58:40.633 --> 58:43.068
Municipal and state authorities, 


58:43.068 --> 58:45.438
neighbors, and many passersby 


58:45.438 --> 58:47.906
have been amazed 
at what they have seen, 


58:47.907 --> 58:50.844
and they have praised 
the brothers working on the project.


58:50.843 --> 58:55.248
Our brothers and sisters 
in Mali send us their love. 


58:55.248 --> 58:59.018
We love them, 
and we love all of you. 


58:59.018 --> 59:01.620
This is JW Broadcasting 


59:01.620 --> 59:11.682
from the world headquarters 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

